-- Singapore-listed Frasers wins backing for $2.4 bln Australand takeover
-- By Byron Kaye
-- Thu Aug 07, 2014 05:09AM EDT
-- None



SYDNEY, Aug 7 (Reuters) - Singapore-listed Frasers Centrepoint Ltd <FRCT.SI> will buy Australia's Australand Property Group <ALZ.AX> for A$2.6 billion ($2.41 billion) after securing shareholder approval late on Thursday.

